subject: Hello dear,
body:
Hello dear,
I am pleased to inform you that a concrete arrangement has been made for
your long-delayed fund to be released any moment from now.
I hope you respond promptly for more details.
Warm regards.
Regards,
Ikuku Idoko.

subject: Re:   Hello dear,
body:
Dear Ikuku Idoko,

Thank you for your email. I am interested in hearing more about this fund release. Could you please provide me with more details?

Best wishes,
Josefina
